text.tspan: The configurations are graded by the tutor based on how clear the
company is modeled in the configuration.
Columns that have to be corrected by the tutor are penalized.
For both, questionnaire and configuration filling, you get the
possibility to improve the answers and configuration based on the
comments made by the tutor. Although you get two marks (one after
the first submission and one after your correction of the results) only
the second mark is relevant for your final grading. As a result, it is
possible the reach the maximum number of points if the correction
of the configuration is done properly.
